  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2719750/" class="title-link">What you see is what you get!</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2719750"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/humvee/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4390089-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/humvee/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蓝色不忧郁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-11-07"
      class="main-meta">2009-11-07 13:38:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2719750_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  What you see is what you get, 简称WYSIWYG,一个计算机术语，对于解释什么是现象学很有用。现象学就是回到事物本身，并剔除掉一些形而上学的解释。  其实整个西方哲学史可以理解为对于being的探索。being也就是essense，本质，Thales认为是水，赫拉克利特认为是或，毕达哥拉斯...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2719750/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 4没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            团结出版社2003版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
